death sentence is a 2007 american action drama film loosely based on the 1975 novel of the same name by brian garfield . directed by james wan , the film stars kevin bacon as nick hume , a man who takes the law into his own hands after his son is murdered by a gang as an initiation ritual . hume must protect his family from the gang 's resulting vengeance . the film premiered on august 31 , 2007 , and was released on dvd on january 8 , 2008 .